{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.1","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:1","prev_osis_id":"Mark.009.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9sus en P\u00e9r\u00e9e. Le divorce<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. Mt 19:1-12. (De 24:1-4. Mt 5:31, 32.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    J\u00e9sus, \u00e9tant parti de l\u00e0, se rendit dans le territoire de la Jud\u00e9e au-del\u00e0 du Jourdain. La foule s\u2019assembla de nouveau pr\u00e8s de lui, et selon sa coutume, il se mit encore \u00e0 l\u2019enseigner.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.2","name":"Marc 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.9.51","name":"Marc 9:51","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.9.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.2","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:2","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Les pharisiens l\u2019abord\u00e8rent; et, pour l\u2019\u00e9prouver, ils lui demand\u00e8rent s\u2019il est permis \u00e0 un homme de r\u00e9pudier sa femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.3","name":"Marc 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.1","name":"Marc 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.3","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:3","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Que vous a prescrit Mo\u00efse?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.4","name":"Marc 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.2","name":"Marc 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.4","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:4","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mo\u00efse, dirent-ils, a permis d\u2019\u00e9crire une lettre de divorce et de r\u00e9pudier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.5","name":"Marc 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.3","name":"Marc 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.5","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:5","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et J\u00e9sus leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est \u00e0 cause de la duret\u00e9 de votre c\u0153ur que Mo\u00efse vous a donn\u00e9 ce pr\u00e9cepte.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.6","name":"Marc 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.4","name":"Marc 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.6","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:6","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais au commencement de la cr\u00e9ation, Dieu fit l\u2019homme et la femme;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.7","name":"Marc 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.5","name":"Marc 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.7","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:7","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">c\u2019est pourquoi l\u2019homme quittera son p\u00e8re et sa m\u00e8re, et s\u2019attachera \u00e0 sa femme,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.8","name":"Marc 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.6","name":"Marc 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.8","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:8","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et les deux deviendront une seule chair. Ainsi ils ne sont plus deux, mais ils sont une seule chair.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.9","name":"Marc 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.7","name":"Marc 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.9","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:9","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Que l\u2019homme donc ne s\u00e9pare pas ce que Dieu a joint.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.10","name":"Marc 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.8","name":"Marc 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.10","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:10","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils furent dans la maison, les disciples l\u2019interrog\u00e8rent encore l\u00e0-dessus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.11","name":"Marc 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.9","name":"Marc 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.11","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:11","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Celui qui r\u00e9pudie sa femme et qui en \u00e9pouse une autre, commet un adult\u00e8re \u00e0 son \u00e9gard;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.12","name":"Marc 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.10","name":"Marc 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.12","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:12","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et si une femme quitte son mari et en \u00e9pouse un autre, elle commet un adult\u00e8re.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.13","name":"Marc 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.11","name":"Marc 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.13","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:13","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les petits enfants<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-16: cf. (Mt 19:13-15. Lu 18:15-17.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\n    On lui amena des petits enfants, afin qu\u2019il les touch\u00e2t. Mais les disciples reprirent ceux qui les amenaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.14","name":"Marc 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.12","name":"Marc 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.14","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:14","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, voyant cela, fut indign\u00e9, et leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Laissez venir \u00e0 moi les petits enfants, et ne les en emp\u00eachez pas;<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">car le royaume de Dieu est pour ceux qui leur ressemblent.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.15","name":"Marc 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.13","name":"Marc 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.15","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:15","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, quiconque ne recevra pas le royaume de Dieu comme un petit enfant n\u2019y entrera point.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.16","name":"Marc 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.14","name":"Marc 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.16","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:16","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Puis il les prit dans ses bras, et les b\u00e9nit, en leur imposant les mains.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.17","name":"Marc 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.15","name":"Marc 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.17","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:17","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le jeune homme riche<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-27: cf. (Mt 19:16-26. Lu 18:18-27.) Mt 6:19-21, 24. Mc 9:43, etc. Ro 10:3.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>\n    Comme J\u00e9sus se mettait en chemin, un homme accourut, et se jetant \u00e0 genoux devant lui: Bon ma\u00eetre, lui demanda-t-il, que dois-je faire pour h\u00e9riter la vie \u00e9ternelle?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.18","name":"Marc 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.16","name":"Marc 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.18","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:18","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>J\u00e9sus lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">Pourquoi m\u2019appelles-tu bon? Il n\u2019y a de bon que Dieu seul.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.19","name":"Marc 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.17","name":"Marc 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.19","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:19","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Tu connais les commandements:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Tu ne commettras point d\u2019adult\u00e8re; tu ne tueras point; tu ne d\u00e9roberas point; tu ne diras point de faux t\u00e9moignage; tu ne feras tort \u00e0 personne; honore ton p\u00e8re et ta m\u00e8re.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.20","name":"Marc 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.18","name":"Marc 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.20","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:20","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Il lui r\u00e9pondit: Ma\u00eetre, j\u2019ai observ\u00e9 toutes ces choses d\u00e8s ma jeunesse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.21","name":"Marc 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.19","name":"Marc 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.21","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:21","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, l\u2019ayant regard\u00e9, l\u2019aima, et lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">Il te manque une chose; va, vends tout ce que tu as, donne-le aux pauvres, et tu auras un tr\u00e9sor dans le ciel. Puis viens, et suis-moi.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.22","name":"Marc 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.20","name":"Marc 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.22","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:22","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mais, afflig\u00e9 de cette parole, cet homme s\u2019en alla tout triste; car il avait de grands biens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.23","name":"Marc 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.21","name":"Marc 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.23","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:23","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, regardant autour de lui, dit \u00e0 ses disciples: <span class=\"wj\">Qu\u2019il sera difficile \u00e0 ceux qui ont des richesses d\u2019entrer dans le royaume de Dieu!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.24","name":"Marc 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.22","name":"Marc 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.24","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:24","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Les disciples furent \u00e9tonn\u00e9s de ce que J\u00e9sus parlait ainsi. Et, reprenant, il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Mes enfants, qu\u2019il est difficile \u00e0 ceux qui se confient dans les richesses d\u2019entrer dans le royaume de Dieu!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.25","name":"Marc 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.23","name":"Marc 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.25","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:25","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il est plus facile \u00e0 un chameau de passer par le trou d\u2019une aiguille qu\u2019\u00e0 un riche d\u2019entrer dans le royaume de Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.26","name":"Marc 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.24","name":"Marc 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.26","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:26","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Les disciples furent encore plus \u00e9tonn\u00e9s, et ils se dirent les uns aux autres; Et qui peut \u00eatre sauv\u00e9?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.27","name":"Marc 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.25","name":"Marc 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.27","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:27","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>J\u00e9sus les regarda, et dit: <span class=\"wj\">Cela est impossible aux hommes, mais non \u00e0 Dieu:<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">car tout est possible \u00e0 Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.28","name":"Marc 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.26","name":"Marc 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.28","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:28","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.029,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019h\u00e9ritage de la vie \u00e9ternelle<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 28-31: cf. (Mt 19:27-30. Lu 18:28-30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>\n    Pierre se mit \u00e0 lui dire; Voici, nous avons tout quitt\u00e9, et nous t\u2019avons suivi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.29","name":"Marc 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.27","name":"Marc 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.29","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:29","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>J\u00e9sus r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, il n\u2019est personne qui, ayant quitt\u00e9, \u00e0 cause de moi et \u00e0 cause de la bonne nouvelle, sa maison, ou ses fr\u00e8res, ou ses s\u0153urs, ou sa m\u00e8re, ou son p\u00e8re, ou ses enfants, ou ses terres,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.30","name":"Marc 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.28","name":"Marc 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.30","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:30","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">ne re\u00e7oive au centuple, pr\u00e9sentement dans ce si\u00e8cle-ci, des maisons, des fr\u00e8res, des s\u0153urs, des m\u00e8res, des enfants, et des terres, avec des pers\u00e9cutions, et, dans le si\u00e8cle \u00e0 venir, la vie \u00e9ternelle.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.31","name":"Marc 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.29","name":"Marc 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.31","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:31","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Plusieurs des premiers seront les derniers, et plusieurs des derniers seront les premiers.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.32","name":"Marc 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.30","name":"Marc 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.32","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:32","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.033,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9sus annonce sa mort et sa r\u00e9surrection<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 32-34: cf. (Mt 20:17-19. Lu 18:31-34.) Mc 8:31-33.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>\n    Ils \u00e9taient en chemin pour monter \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et J\u00e9sus allait devant eux. Les disciples \u00e9taient troubl\u00e9s, et le suivaient avec crainte. Et J\u00e9sus prit de nouveau les douze aupr\u00e8s de lui, et commen\u00e7a \u00e0 leur dire ce qui devait lui arriver:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.33","name":"Marc 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.31","name":"Marc 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.33","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:33","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Voici, nous montons \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et le Fils de l\u2019homme sera livr\u00e9 aux principaux sacrificateurs et aux scribes. Ils le condamneront \u00e0 mort, et ils le livreront aux pa\u00efens,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.34","name":"Marc 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.32","name":"Marc 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.34","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:34","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">qui se moqueront de lui, cracheront sur lui, le battront de verges, et le feront mourir; et, trois jours apr\u00e8s, il ressuscitera.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.35","name":"Marc 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.33","name":"Marc 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.35","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:35","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.036,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Demande des fils de Z\u00e9b\u00e9d\u00e9e<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 35-45: cf. Mt 20:20-28. (Lu 22:24-27. Jn 13:3-17.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>\n    Les fils de Z\u00e9b\u00e9d\u00e9e, Jacques et Jean, s\u2019approch\u00e8rent de J\u00e9sus, et lui dirent: Ma\u00eetre, nous voudrions que tu fisses pour nous ce que nous te demanderons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.36","name":"Marc 10:36","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.34","name":"Marc 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.36","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:36","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Que voulez-vous que je fasse pour vous?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.37","name":"Marc 10:37","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.35","name":"Marc 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.37","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:37","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Accorde-nous, lui dirent-ils, d\u2019\u00eatre assis l\u2019un \u00e0 ta droite et l\u2019autre \u00e0 ta gauche, quand tu seras dans ta gloire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.38","name":"Marc 10:38","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.36","name":"Marc 10:36","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.38","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:38","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>J\u00e9sus leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Vous ne savez ce que vous demandez. Pouvez-vous boire la coupe que je dois boire, ou \u00eatre baptis\u00e9s du bapt\u00eame<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">dont je dois \u00eatre baptis\u00e9?<\/span> Nous le pouvons, dirent-ils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.39","name":"Marc 10:39","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.37","name":"Marc 10:37","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.39","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:39","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Et J\u00e9sus leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Il est vrai que vous boirez la coupe que je dois boire, et que vous serez baptis\u00e9s du bapt\u00eame dont je dois \u00eatre baptis\u00e9;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.40","name":"Marc 10:40","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.38","name":"Marc 10:38","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.40","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:40","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">mais pour ce qui est d\u2019\u00eatre assis \u00e0 ma droite ou \u00e0 ma gauche, cela ne d\u00e9pend pas de moi, et ne sera donn\u00e9 qu\u2019\u00e0 ceux \u00e0 qui cela est r\u00e9serv\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.41","name":"Marc 10:41","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.39","name":"Marc 10:39","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.41","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:41","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Les dix, ayant entendu cela, commenc\u00e8rent \u00e0 s\u2019indigner contre Jacques et Jean.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.42","name":"Marc 10:42","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.40","name":"Marc 10:40","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.42","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:42","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>J\u00e9sus les appela, et leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Vous savez<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">que ceux qu\u2019on regarde comme les chefs des nations les tyrannisent, et que les grands les dominent.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.43","name":"Marc 10:43","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.41","name":"Marc 10:41","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.43","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:43","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il n\u2019en est pas de m\u00eame au milieu de vous. Mais quiconque veut \u00eatre grand parmi vous, qu\u2019il soit votre serviteur;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.44","name":"Marc 10:44","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.42","name":"Marc 10:42","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.44","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:44","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et quiconque veut \u00eatre le premier parmi vous, qu\u2019il soit l\u2019esclave de tous.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.45","name":"Marc 10:45","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.43","name":"Marc 10:43","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.45","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:45","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car le Fils de l\u2019homme est venu,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">non pour \u00eatre servi, mais pour servir et<\/span><span class=\"wj\">donner sa vie comme la ran\u00e7on de plusieurs.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.46","name":"Marc 10:46","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.44","name":"Marc 10:44","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.46","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:46","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.047,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019aveugle Bartim\u00e9e gu\u00e9ri \u00e0 J\u00e9richo<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 46-53: cf. (Mt 20:29-34. Lu 18:35-43.) Ps 146:8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>\n    Ils arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9richo. Et, lorsque J\u00e9sus en sortit, avec ses disciples et une assez grande foule, le fils de Tim\u00e9e, Bartim\u00e9e, mendiant aveugle, \u00e9tait assis au bord du chemin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.47","name":"Marc 10:47","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.45","name":"Marc 10:45","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.47","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:47","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Il entendit que c\u2019\u00e9tait J\u00e9sus de Nazareth, et il se mit \u00e0 crier; Fils de David, J\u00e9sus aie piti\u00e9 de moi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.48","name":"Marc 10:48","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.46","name":"Marc 10:46","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.48","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:48","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Plusieurs le reprenaient, pour le faire taire; mais il criait beaucoup plus fort; Fils de David, aie piti\u00e9 de moi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.49","name":"Marc 10:49","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.47","name":"Marc 10:47","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.49","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:49","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>J\u00e9sus s\u2019arr\u00eata, et dit: <span class=\"wj\">Appelez-le.<\/span> Ils appel\u00e8rent l\u2019aveugle, en lui disant: Prends courage, l\u00e8ve-toi, il t\u2019appelle.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.50","name":"Marc 10:50","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.48","name":"Marc 10:48","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.50","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:50","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup>L\u2019aveugle jeta son manteau, et, se levant d\u2019un bond, vint vers J\u00e9sus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.51","name":"Marc 10:51","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.49","name":"Marc 10:49","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.51","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:51","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.052,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, prenant la parole, lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">Que veux-tu que je te fasse?<\/span> Rabbouni, lui r\u00e9pondit l\u2019aveugle, que je recouvre la vue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.52","name":"Marc 10:52","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.52"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.50","name":"Marc 10:50","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"52","lastverse":"52","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.52","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.52","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:52","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.010.053,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.52\" class=\"v\">52<\/sup>Et J\u00e9sus lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">Va,<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">ta foi t\u2019a sauv\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.53","name":"Marc 10:53","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.53"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.51","name":"Marc 10:51","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"53","lastverse":"53","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.53","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.53","label":"","reference":"Marc 10:53","prev_osis_id":"Mark.010.052,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.011.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.10.53\" class=\"v\">53<\/sup>Aussit\u00f4t il recouvra la vue, et suivit J\u00e9sus dans le chemin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.10","name":"Marc 10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.11.1","name":"Marc 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.11.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.10.52","name":"Marc 10:52","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.10.52"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb7de0641.64571753');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb7de0641.64571753\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb7de0641.64571753","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb7de0641.64571753'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb7de0641.64571753\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}